# Attack 04 – User and Administrator Discovery

## Objective

Simulate attacker discovery activity.

## Attack

Executed Windows discovery commands including:

- net user
- net localgroup administrators
- whoami

## Detection

- Wazuh Rule: 92039
- Alert: Net.exe account discovery command initiated

## MITRE ATT&CK

- T1087 – Account Discovery

## Investigation

Verified execution through Windows process creation logs in Wazuh.

## Outcome

Discovery commands were successfully detected.
